{"tid":549443,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】激運票獵人 Day173 3/2【MHW】","createTime":"2018-02-03T15:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T18:31:18.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49cc6fe5517f7ad9c25b26f91d5722d289b553cd","tid":549443,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=z8jBNQZosMeRET1HuIIOQpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2fc1b06d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=z8jBNQZosMeRET1HuIIOQpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=945ada9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"b2849ae6eeaa7cbcfa37a78eec5016b06c3635b1","tid":549443,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8cb354a4efaa71a22eb3d613166ba485134e7a","tid":549443,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dd64279ccb589c2425ed6fba0438a282c76f9b","tid":549443,"uid"